item.title: Need help i think this is simply thing i just dunno how to do it =)
item.dc:creator: @pizza_pie pizza pie
item.description:
@pizza_pie wrote:

find this:

public void WriteWildyLevel()

replace that with

public void WriteWildyLevel()
{
checkwildy2();
if(inwildy2 && !nonWild())
{
outStream.createFrame(208);
outStream.writeWordBigEndian_dup(197);
sendQuest("@red@Pk Zone", 199);
leftwild = 1;
}
else if(nonWild() && inwildy2 && leftwild == 1)
{
outStream.createFrame(208);
outStream.writeWordBigEndian_dup(197);
sendQuest("@gre@Safe", 199);
}
}

and change “@gre@Safe” to whatever you want and “@red@Pk Zone” to whatever you want
